## Architecture

- FastAPI backend serves public_html/ as the frontend.
- News refresh: every 5 minutes via background task.
- Trends refresh: every 20 minutes via background task (staggered 30s after startup).
- SQLite cache: stories table + trend_cache table + trend_history table + source_locations table.
- On startup: stale trend_cache entries older than 24h are automatically cleared.

