  NewsAPI       → NEWSAPI_KEY env var

## Key design rules

- public_html/ uses JetBrains Mono + Inter, dark surfaces (#0b0f0b), military aesthetic.
- Do not make major UX changes — match existing aesthetic when adding features.
- New UI elements should use existing CSS variables and button/pill styles.
- The .gitignore excludes project_rollup.db, __pycache__, *.pyc, _preview_server.py.

## Deployment

- Hosted on Render. The DB is regenerated on each cold start.
- Do not commit project_rollup.db.
- _preview_server.py is dev-only — do not deploy.

## Syntax checks before pushing

- Python: py_compile app.py
- JS:     node --check public_html/js/dashboard.js
